## Bug Fixes & Technical Debt Resolutions

| Bug Description | Root Cause | Resolution |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Ghost Enemies** | Event subscriptions weren't cleaned up between waves. | Implemented `OnDisable` cleanup and ensured `WaveSpawner` clears lists on reset. |
| **Type Mismatch Error** | Linking Scene objects into Prefab assets in the Inspector. | Refactored scripts to find references (like the Player) at runtime using tags or Singletons. |
| **Animator Crash (NullRef)** | Corrupted Library folder / Metadata mismatch. | Performed a full Library folder deletion and re-import to rebuild the asset database. |
| **Jumping Health Bar** | Inconsistent health variables between Controller and GameManager. | Synced all UI updates to pull strictly from the `GameManager` source of truth. |
| **Broken UI Layout** | Missing UI Anchors and improper Canvas Scaler mode. | Set Canvas Scaler to "Scale With Screen Size" and anchored HUD elements to corners. |
| **Static Collectibles** | `Quaternion.identity` was overriding prefab rotation. | Changed rotation logic to apply a local Euler rotation over time for the spin effect. |
